data.description: This beautifully updated house is a true gem, offering perfect charm located right in the middle of Fort Walton Beach. The open living room and kitchen floor plan creates a welcoming and spacious atmosphere. Whether you're hosting family gatherings or simply enjoying a quiet night in, this layout is perfect for any occasion. Brand new roof installed October 2023. The wiring has been completely replaced. Major Items: 2015 HVAC. 2021 Gas Hot Water Heater & Double pane windows. One of the standout features of this home is the master bedroom and bathroom addition, completed in 2022. This spacious retreat offers over 250 sqft of private space separated from the other bedrooms.  If you love outdoor living, you're in for a treat. This house boasts a screened-in sunroom, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet morning coffee. The large workshop in the backyard provides ample space for your hobbies, DIY projects, or storage needs. For those sunny days, you'll appreciate the 2022 addition of the above-ground pool. It's a great spot to cool off and soak up the Florida sunshine. Location is key, and this house has it all. It's just minutes away from Hurlburt Field, Eglin Air Force Base, beautiful beaches, shopping centers, and a wide range of entertainment options. Whether you're a new family looking for a forever home or an investor seeking a short-term or long-term rental property, this house offers tremendous value and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully renovated Fort Walton Beach house your new home. It's the perfect place to create lasting memories and enjoy the Florida lifestyle to the fullest.
